card.title: The Terrible Two Get Worse: The Terrible Two, Book 2

metadata.author: Mac Barnett and Jory John
metadata.description: On their own, pranksters Miles and Niles were pretty devious. Now that theyve formed a pranking duo, theyre terrible! But their powers will be tested when their favorite nemesis, Principal Barkin, is replaced by his stern and cunning father, former Principal Barkin. Now Miles and Niles will do just about anything to get their old antagonist backincluding pranking alongside him. From authors and friends Mac Barnett and Jory John comes the second installment in the series that celebrates inventiveness, friendship, and the power of teamworkfor good, or for terrible.
